<h2>A Pediatrics WebServer</h2>

These World Wide Web pages are dedicated to the dissemination
of on-line information for pediatricians and others
interested in child health. The URL for this page is:<P>

<B>http://www.lhl.uab.edu/pedinfo</B><P>

